foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: After reviewing their databases, Admin, C&LA, GC, HRM, OAL, OIT, ORM, OSDBU, VBA, and VHA updated the number of requests pending as of the start of the Fiscal Year.

foia:ProcessedAppealSection.foia:FootnoteText: After reviewing its database, GC updated the number of appeals pending as of the start of the Fiscal Year.

foia:ProcessedRequestComparisonSection.foia:FootnoteText: After reviewing their databases, all components, except for ODASB, OSDBU, OSP, P&P, and PA updated the number of requests received from last year's annual report. Additionally, after reviewing their databases, all components, except for CFM, ODASB, OSP, P&P, and PA updated the number of requests processed from last year's annual report.

foia:BackloggedRequestComparisonSection.foia:FootnoteText: After reviewing their databases, Admin, C&LA, GC, HRM, OAL, OASP&IA, OIT, ORM, OSDBU, SEC, VBA, and VHA updated the number of requests backlogged from the previous Fiscal Year.

foia:ProcessedAppealComparisonSection.foia:FootnoteText: After reviewing its database, GC updated the number of appeals received and processed from last year's annual report.

foia:BackloggedAppealComparisonSection.foia:FootnoteText: After reviewing its database, GC updated the number of backlogged appeals from the previous Fiscal Year.
